HEADWORD: Cant hook
<hw>Cant" hook`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A wooden lever with a movable
iron hook. hear the end; -- used for canting or turning over heavy logs,
etc.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark> <rj><au>Bartlett.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

